# Running STT model locally

### Setting up Python environment

```shell
python3 -m venv .  
source bin/activate
```

### Installing 3rd party libraries

```shell
pip install transformers
pip install librosa
pip install torch torchvision
 pip install soundfile
pip install fastapi
pip install uvicorn
```

### Running the API
```shell
python main.py
```

http://127.0.0.1:3008



### Calling the STT model via RESTful API with audio file in the request

```shell
curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:3008/transcribe -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"audio": ""}'
```
